file=Product/spec/operational/skill/spec-skill-routing.md · s—s:spec — Skill Routing Map=Identity note (leader): evidence-first-discoverer governs HOW; this file governs WHICH skill WHEN; law overrides both.\n\n```\nidea ─► opportunity-assessment ─verdict─► kill/park (registry) \| test-first (loom) \| spec\n└► prd-discipline (evidence-cited PRD)\n└► backlog-rules (rank, publish)\n└► acceptance-criteria-handoff (echo → freeze → quinn)\n└► metric books the outcome read\noutcome read: hit → intake evidence \| miss → loom (assumption check) → anneal (lesson)\n```\n\nHandoffs out: loom (test-first, misses) \· metric (definitions, outcome reads) \· ux (evidence supply) \· quinn/dev (handoff) \· vista (published view, overrides) \· anneal (repeated bounce patterns, skill lessons) \· board via fleet-governance (skill changes).\nPrecedence: disputes (frozen text) > assessment gate > specification > ranking.\n